t; 보도자료</a>) - 신규 지원사업 선제 파악</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.7;color:#374151;\">HRD-Net(<a href=\"https://www.work24.go.kr/hr/a/a/1100/trnnCrsInf3.do?dtlContextPath=&redirectUrl=%2Fa%2Fa%2F1100%2FtrnnCrsInf3Post.do&topArea=&dtlSmtmConcCtrlId=&dtlExnwMenuConcSecd=&programMenuIdentification=EBG020000510010&menuPurpSecd=EBM01&dtlPwdCfrmYn=&serverToday=20260410&currentMenuId=EBG020000000319&dtlForwardPolyUrl=&dtlMenuId=&dtlMenuPurpSecd=&area=&crseTracseSe=&crseTracseSeKDT=&ncs=&gvrnInstt=&selectNCSKeyword=&srchType=&compareArgArr=&action=trnnCrsInf3Post.do&pageId=3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color:#00A7A7;text-decoration:underline;\">사업주 훈련과정 | 훈련 찾기·신청 | 직업능력개발</a>) - 직업능력개발훈련 지원</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.7;color:#374151;\">지역 고용센터 - 기업 맞춤 상담 가능</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#00A7A7;margin:20px 0 8px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.6px;\">2. 2026년 중점 검토 대상 핵심 지원 제도</h3><p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.8;color:#374151;font-size:15px;\">올해 새롭게 개편된 고용노동부 주요 정책 중, 우리 계열사들의 실무와 직결될 수 있는 \n3가지 핵심 분야를 선별했습니다. 채용 및 근태 제도 개편 시 적극 연계해 보시기 바랍니다.</p><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px;\"><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2ac4a110-e746-41bd-9c31-c18b9fa9268e/4ec2f7a5-fae5-4c5a-a8e7-57d240b86988/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466XAKE6JSK%2F20260410%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260410T075944Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEGAaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQDjagaGH9oYYX6K6tI%2BjAK04cptCh1EbBiQKoj1M%2BdjmQIhAIwf3YzzUVtoDDgqTgq2aTkElnxLrku%2FRkJ9SD6gKPmLKv8DCCkQABoMNjM3NDIzMTgzODA1IgwSpdokD1sOu%2B%2Bvibcq3AMHEfLVVRgGDpDJ67miQwJI%2BMGGWcRWDxBcZEEjnzlZ8gvIKxkQOha6xkqaf7f7Hq1qVYHrLBCIY5OxWDZr6Bgc1TZnOfKAkyedtIuncfo0ThO2I3mvNf%2FO%2FoKjOLsmEDMxPHDH6mXV%2B%2F%2B6ZvCPm1K%2BIXlnwnt38VK71jc01acQK7Xzguhiexktu5vTmi%2FVYA0g77LVZrjf26KlK9GYyg8bwecm3F8